  "detailed_description": "Are you bored? Then step into the world of Fantasy Monster Clicker! Enjoy and explore a world full of upgrades, levels, monsters and bosses.<br><br><strong>Game Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrades</h2><li> Beat monsters and bosses and upgrade yourself with the coins you earn<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554770/extras/ce0e76bb705c3abddc8c7236749969b6.poster.avif?t=1695026921\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554770/extras/ce0e76bb705c3abddc8c7236749969b6.webm?t=1695026921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554770/extras/ce0e76bb705c3abddc8c7236749969b6.mp4?t=1695026921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse Chapters</h2></li><li>Traverse between chapters with distinct themes, altering the look and feel of your gameplay. Each chapter introduces new monsters and surprises.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554770/extras/d8de64c551106c8ec5377eac38dc2c19.poster.avif?t=1695026921\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554770/extras/d8de64c551106c8ec5377eac38dc2c19.webm?t=1695026921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554770/extras/d8de64c551106c8ec5377eac38dc2c19.mp4?t=1695026921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Monsters</h2></li><li>Battle against a thrilling array of monsters and bosses that will test your wit and clicker skills. Will you emerge victorious against these formidable foes?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554770/extras/5fc3ee63b70cfb5fcb842560019b8979.poster.avif?t=1695026921\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554770/extras/5fc3ee63b70cfb5fcb842560019b8979.webm?t=1695026921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554770/extras/5fc3ee63b70cfb5fcb842560019b8979.mp4?t=1695026921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>In Fantasy Clicker Monster, you'll find enjoyment in upgrading and enhancing , all while exercising your clicker skills. Make upgrades and defeat stronger monsters and bosses",
