_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554770/extras/5fc3ee63b70cfb5fcb842560019b8979.poster.avif?t=1695026921\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554770/extras/5fc3ee63b70cfb5fcb842560019b8979.webm?t=1695026921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554770/extras/5fc3ee63b70cfb5fcb842560019b8979.mp4?t=1695026921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>In Fantasy Clicker Monster, you'll find enjoyment in upgrading and enhancing , all while exercising your clicker skills. Make upgrades and defeat stronger monsters and bosses",
